tro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/99f288af90ca26eda74f2293e3eccc78?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 405279}, "last_reply_by": "pengtdyd", "last_touched": 1628005859, "title": "公司最近要给我们换办公设备，显示器的价格大概在 8k，键盘鼠标没有上限，求推荐，本人码农", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/793314", "created": 1627957460, "content": "https://item.m.jd.com/product/100003422312.html", "content_rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://item.m.jd.com/product/100003422312.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://item.m.jd.com/product/100003422312.html</a></p>\n", "last_modified": 1627957460, "replies": 45, "id": 793314}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1583044904", "name": "windows", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1583044904", "title": "Windows", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows", "topics": 2153, "footer": "", "header": "Windows, not walls.", "title_alternative": "Windows", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1583044904", "stars": 718, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 360, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "dingyx99", "website": "", "github": "dingyx99", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/54e4/e636/341652_mini.png?m=1583678582", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/dingyx99", "tagline": "大切な人と、いつかまた巡り会えますように。", "twitter": "", "created": 1534393147, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/54e4/e636/341652_mini.png?m=1583678582", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/54e4/e636/341652_mini.png?m=1583678582", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 341652}, "last_reply_by": "black201w", "last_touched": 1627972781, "title": "Windows 365 初体验", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/793286", "created": 1627951666, "content": "手头的订阅可以用两个月的 Trial，就干脆下单了一个试试看\r\n\r\n（实际上所有 SKU 好像都可以试用两个月，但是你必须是一个订阅的全局管理员才能整，个人 Microsoft 帐户现阶段是不能买的）\r\n\r\n![]( https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNgy1gt3arcbzoej315a0u075e.jpg)\r\n\r\n订阅下单后，需要去 Admin Portal 手动分配许可证，之后在 Office Portal 就能找到入口\r\n\r\n![]( https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNgy1gt3b69xrxij30hu0r20tr.jpg)\r\n\r\n进去之后很简洁，没有多余功能\r\n\r\n![]( https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNgy1gt3b6vjreoj316f0u00ui.jpg)\r\n\r\n如果需要用 RDP，需要用提供的订阅链接去官方的远程桌面添加工作区，同时登录你的账号\r\n\r\n![]( https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNgy1gt3b7wiob0j31l60swtc2.jpg)\r\n\r\n碎碎念：初始化设备太慢了，都快半个小时了还没好，等会儿好了进去体验后继续 append", "content_rendered": "<p>手头的订阅可以用两个月的 Trial，就干脆下单了一个试试看</p>\n<p>（实际上所有 SKU 好像都可以试用两个月，但是你必须是一个订阅的全局管理员才能整，个人 Microsoft 帐户现阶段是不能买的）</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNgy1gt3arcbzoej315a0u075e.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>订阅下单后，需要去 Admin Portal 手动分配许可证，之后在 Office Portal 就能找到入口</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNgy1gt3b69xrxij30hu0r20tr.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>进去之后很简洁，没有多余功能</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNgy1gt3b6vjreoj316f0u00ui.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>如果需要用 RDP，需要用提供的订阅链接去官方的远程桌面添加工作区，同时登录你的账号</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNgy1gt3b7wiob0j31l60swtc2.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>碎碎念：初始化设备太慢了，都快半个小时了还没好，等会儿好了进去体验后继续 append</p>\n", "last_modified": 1627951666, "replies": 43, "id": 793286}]